{"tid":477672,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"18 - 24 Whatsapp Group","createTime":"2017-11-23T08:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-04T03:43:29.000Z","uid":53331,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aa2013d86bbd17a5094f8dee06287d6f2a7a65d9","tid":477672,"uid":53331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T08:56:04.000Z","msg":"時移世易 18至24 Whatsapp Group 乃 18至22 Whatsapp Group延續。 <br />\n<br />\n我們希望關系和諧，因始沒有你我之分，更沒有兩登之分。<br />\n<br />\n都開左一段日子 係一個有秩序又開心既Group <br />\n<br />\n之前填過既可以在填多次 順便睇睇張Form既聲明及條款細則<br />\n<br />\n張Form會開到11月30日 填form後兩星期內如有幸抽中會有專人通知入Group 多謝各位一路以來既支持 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nextravel.hk/even/18-24-whatsapp-group/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nextravel.hk%2Feven%2F18-24-whatsapp-group%2F&d=vvZaVjXVMljUr7jM103PqE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=3e49d2a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nextravel.hk/even/18-24-whatsapp-group/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n18至24 Whatsapp Group為會員而設，暫時只限相關會員加入。謝謝！。<br />\n<br />\n***為確保言論自由不被惡意功擊/侵犯及Group內成員及相關私穩，請填寫表格前細閱所有聲明條款及細則***<br />\n<br />\n再次感謝各位一年來的支持<br />\n<br />\n感謝<a href=\"http://nextravel.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextravel.hk&d=vvZaVjXVMljUr7jM103PqE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=96579bf2\" target=\"_blank\">nextravel.hk</a>提供新方式供表格使用"},{"pid":"2a578c13f4c4c271995c7e58b0f482b86b43ef42","tid":477672,"uid":53331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T00:06:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64931e709c8554baf1b6e538cb892993bbad35f7","tid":477672,"uid":53331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T17:53:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3888954262fa26bc42ed0da074edf4c829fd80","tid":477672,"uid":53331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T01:55:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gi